          "intendedUse": "Empathy-building: Helps students understand the challenges a college student who relies on university internet might struggle with throttling and slow internet speeds. \nDiscussion on net neutrality: Highlights how ISPs prioritizing big companies could harm education sector. \nProblem-solving activity: Encourages students to brainstorm ways to improve rural Internet access.\n",
